name: Experiment Or Die #59
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. Years ago I made a trade with a friend of mine. I gave him a 3A figure and he acquired a rare pair of Dunks for me...but the person that ended up selling us the Dunks scammed me and I never received the package. A Sour Grapes kind of moment. Who is responsible for the shoes?? Needless to say he just went ahead and secured another pair...and they were and are my favorite pair of Dunks of all time. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
